doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Contact Query Response
  body(style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background:#f5f5f5;")
    
    // Main Container
    div(style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);")

      h2(style="color:#1f8ef1; margin-bottom: 10px;") Contact Query Update

      p(style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;")
        | Hi #{name},

      p(style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;")
        | We have reviewed your contact request. Below is the update regarding your query.

      h3(style="margin: 15px 0 5px; color:#444;") Your Query:
      p(style="background:#f5f7fa; padding:12px 15px; border-radius:6px; margin-bottom: 20px;")
        | #{query}

      h3(style="margin: 15px 0 5px; color:#444;") Our Response:
      p(style="background:#e8f4ff; padding:12px 15px; border-radius:6px; border-left:5px solid #1f8ef1; margin-bottom: 20px; white-space:pre-line;")
        | #{solution}

      p(style="font-size: 15px; margin-top: 20px;")
        | If you have more questions, feel free to reply to this email.

      p(style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 15px; color:#555;")
        | Thanks,
        br
        | The #{appName} Team
